snippet.title: Trailer Super Vadimka VII: The Nightmares of The Current Continue (2023)
snippet.description:
Super Vadimka VII: The Nightmares of The Current Continue" is the final game of the original "Super Vadimka" series. The game was developed by VadimBallzGame. Also Special Thanks for HyperTheLoopa420.
The story tells how, after the events of the sixth part, Dr. Kulik ressucured from the dead and gathered villains.
